"navVariant":"base","head":{"title":"Contract Claims | Moonstone Advocates","description":"Contracts can be written or verbal and cover a wide range of arrangements, from the supply of goods to the delivery of services. When a contract is breached, the impact can be significant. Whether you're dealing with lost income, business disruption, or a claim made against you, we'll help you understand your position and take practical steps to protect your interests as efficiently and effectively as possible.","ogTitle":"Contract Claims | Moonstone Advocates","ogDescription":"Contracts can be written or verbal and cover a wide range of arrangements, from the supply of goods to the delivery of services. When a contract is breached, the impact can be significant. Whether you're dealing with lost income, business disruption, or a claim made against you, we'll help you understand your position and take practical steps to protect your interests as efficiently and effectively as possible.","ogType":"website","twitterCard":"summary_large_image","canonical":"contract-claims.html","jsonLd":["{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Contract Claims\",\n  \"description\": \"Contracts can be written or verbal and cover a wide range of arrangements, from the supply of goods to the delivery of services. When a contract is breached, the impact can be significant. Whether you're dealing with lost income, business disruption, or a claim made against you, we'll help you understand your position and take practical steps to protect your interests as efficiently and effectively as possible.\",\n  \"url\": \"/for-individuals/dispute-resolution/contract-claims\",\n  \"inLanguage\": \"en\",\n  \"breadcrumb\": {\n    \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n    \"itemListElement\": [\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"ListItem\",\n        \"position\": 1,\n        \"name\": \"Home\",\n        \"item\": \"/\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"ListItem\",\n        \"position\": 2,\n        \"name\": \"For individuals\",\n        \"item\": \"/for-individuals\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"ListItem\",\n        \"position\": 3,\n        \"name\": \"Dispute Resolution\",\n        \"item\": \"/for-individuals/dispute-resolution\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"ListItem\",\n        \"position\": 4,\n        \"name\": \"Contract Claims\"\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"provider\": {\n    \"@type\": \"LegalService\",\n    \"name\": \"MOONSTONE ADVOCATES\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.moonstone.co.ug\",\n    \"address\": {\n      \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n      \"streetAddress\": \"City Point, 29 King Street\",\n      \"addressLocality\": \"Kampala\",\n      \"postalCode\": \"LS1 2HL\",\n      \"addressCountry\": \"GB\"\n    },\n    \"telephone\": \"0113 207 0000\"\n  },\n  \"about\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Service\",\n    \"serviceType\": \"Dispute Resolution\",\n    \"description\": \"Contracts can be written or verbal and cover a wide range of arrangements, from the supply of goods to the delivery of services. When a contract is breached, the impact can be significant. Whether you're dealing with lost income, business disruption, or a claim made against you, we'll help you understand your position and take practical steps to protect your interests as efficiently and effectively as possible.\",\n    \"provider\": {\n      \"@type\": \"LegalService\",\n      \"name\": \"MOONSTONE ADVOCATES\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"mainEntity\": {\n    \"@type\": \"FAQPage\",\n    \"mainEntity\": [\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"Is there a time limit for bringing a contract claim?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"Yes. In most cases, you must issue a claim within six years of the breach taking place. Acting early gives you the best chance of preserving evidence and resolving the dispute effectively.\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"Is issuing a claim at court my only option?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"No. Court proceedings aren't always the right solution. We'll work with you to explore alternative ways to resolve the dispute, including negotiation, mediation and other forms of dispute resolution where appropriate.\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"Will I need to attend court?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"Most cases are resolved without the need to attend court. If the matter can't be resolved and a trial is required, you'll usually need to attend court to give evidence. If that happens, we'll support and guide you throughout the process.\"\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  },\n  \"datePublished\": \"2026-07-08T12:22:53.447Z\",\n  \"dateModified\": \"2026-07-08T10:50:08.273Z\"\n}"]},"blocks":[{"tag":"main","attrs":{"className":"main-wrapper"},"html":"<header data-wf--02-standard-header--variant=\"dark\" data-wf-component-id=\"949280b8-8e72-c6a2-5bfc-7cfb2eeda9b8\" data-wf-variant-state=\"8c1228b1-e5f0-eb03-34af-789b7e070b17\" class=\"section_header w-variant-8c1228b1-e5f0-eb03-34af-789b7e070b17\"><div class=\"padding-global is-page-top\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"simple_header-component\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"simple_header_grid\"><div id=\"w-node-_8b2fa05c-57cd-b490-ced6-6fac2cf8719e-2eeda9b8\" class=\"simple_header_grid-left\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h1 class=\"heading-style-h1\">Contract Claims</h1></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Contracts can be written or verbal and cover a wide range of arrangements, from the supply of goods to the delivery of services. When a contract is breached, the impact can be significant. Whether you&#x27;re dealing with lost income, business disruption, or a claim made against you, we&#x27;ll help you understand your position and take practical steps to protect your interests as efficiently and effectively as possible.</p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a arrow-rotate=\"trigger\" data-btn-hover=\"\" data-theme=\"primary\" href=\"/contact\" class=\"btn is-icon w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Speak to an expert</p></div><div btn-arrow=\"right\" class=\"arrow is-button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div></a></div></div></div><div id=\"w-node-_8b2fa05c-57cd-b490-ced6-6fac2cf871aa-2eeda9b8\" class=\"simple_header_grid-right\"><div class=\"simple-header_image-wrapper\"><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/68b448d4e0ae8eda7aa37155_placeholder-image.svg\" alt=\"Grey image placeholder with image icon centralised\" class=\"simple-header_image\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"simple_header-component\"><div class=\"padding-section-xsmall\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div data-wf--breadcrumb-original--variant=\"base\" class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">Home</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/for-individuals\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">For individuals</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_current-page\">Contract Claims</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"listing_shape-wrapper w-variant-8c1228b1-e5f0-eb03-34af-789b7e070b17\"><div lottie=\"target-load\" class=\"header_shape is-standard\" data-w-id=\"5d828c84-1f1c-1e38-bfb3-80ffb8d04940\" data-animation-type=\"lottie\" data-src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69db9824cf9ff19dd03c1c29_08fdbca2c62ae345f765f433c8401fe4_Moonstone_V_Blue.json\" data-loop=\"0\" data-direction=\"1\" data-autoplay=\"1\" data-is-ix2-target=\"0\" data-renderer=\"svg\" data-default-duration=\"0\" data-duration=\"0\" data-loading=\"lazy\"></div></div><div class=\"simple-header_background-image-wrapper\"><div class=\"image-overlay-layer\"></div><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/68b448d4e0ae8eda7aa37155_placeholder-image.svg\" alt=\"Grey image placeholder with image icon centralised\" class=\"simple-header_background-image\"></div></header><section class=\"section_benefit-grid_layout\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"benefit-grid_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid benefit-grid_list\"><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4><strong>Understanding the contract </strong></h4><p>We&#x27;ll review the contract alongside any relevant correspondence and discussions that took place before it was agreed. By identifying the key obligations and responsibilities early on, we can give you clear advice on the strength of your position and the options available to you.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Misrepresentation </h4><p>Sometimes the issues in dispute stem from what happened before the contract was even signed. If one party made a false statement of fact or law that persuaded the other party to enter into the contract, this could amount to a misrepresentation. We&#x27;ll assess at an early stage whether the breach of contract arises from an actionable misrepresentation.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4><strong>Assessing the breach</strong> </h4><p>Not every breach of contract has the same consequences. We will consider the nature of the breach and the consequences of that. To help us build the right strategy</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Termination of the contract </h4><p>In some situations, bringing a contract to an end may be the best way forward. We&#x27;ll explore the options available to you and advise whether terminating the agreement could help you achieve your objectives whilst protecting your legal position.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Mitigation </h4><p>If you&#x27;ve suffered a loss because of a breach of contract, you&#x27;re expected to take reasonable steps to reduce that loss where possible. This is known as a “duty to mitigate”. We&#x27;ll guide you through the practical steps you can take and help you put yourself in the strongest position to recover any losses you&#x27;ve suffered.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty w-richtext\"></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty w-richtext\"></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty w-richtext\"></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty w-richtext\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section_accordion\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"faq6_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid faq6_content\"><div class=\"faq6_content-left\"><h2>Questions we’re often asked</h2><div class=\"margin-top margin-small\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"button is-secondary w-button\">Speak to an expert</a></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_list\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid faq6_list-grid\"><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f7d\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>Is there a time limit for bringing a contract claim?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>Yes. In most cases, you must issue a claim within six years of the breach taking place. Acting early gives you the best chance of preserving evidence and resolving the dispute effectively.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f88\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>Is issuing a claim at court my only option?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>No. Court proceedings aren&#x27;t always the right solution. We&#x27;ll work with you to explore alternative ways to resolve the dispute, including negotiation, mediation and other forms of dispute resolution where appropriate.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f93\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>Will I need to attend court?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>Most cases are resolved without the need to attend court. If the matter can&#x27;t be resolved and a trial is required, you&#x27;ll usually need to attend court to give evidence. If that happens, we&#x27;ll support and guide you throughout the process.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"section_testimonial\"><div class=\"w-embed\"><style>\n.section_testimonial:has(.w-dyn-empty) {\n  display: none;\n}\n</style></div><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-1-card-slider\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_instance\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation-wrapper\"><div class=\"testimonial_icon-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/69010fb7542aa2ee07e42406_quote-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"testimonial_icon\"></div><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation\"><button fs-slider-element=\"previous\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M14.71 15.88L10.83 12l3.88-3.88a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41-1.41L8.71 11.3a.996.996 0 0 0 0 1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39 1.02.39 1.41 0c.38-.39.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button><button fs-slider-element=\"next\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M9.29 15.88L13.17 12L9.29 8.12a.996.996 0 1 1 1.41-1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39.39 1.02 0 1.41L10.7 17.3a.996.996 0 0 1-1.41 0c-.38-.39-.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Thank you to Danielle for all her effort during this process, obviously not one I wanted to be in, but Danielle has made it a much clearer and less stressful one.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Just wanted to say that Danielle&#x27;s helpfulness, generosity of time, and straightforward way of discussing things so far have already been really refreshing regarding this awkward process. It is really appreciated.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Paula was brilliant throughout, providing help, support and advice during an incredibly long and drawn-out situation that should never have reached that point in the first place. I’m truly grateful for everything she did.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I was impressed by the team at Black Solicitors LLP. Every member of staff I dealt with was pleasant and professional, demonstrating a clear commitment to helping me rather than just driving up costs.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">My first time using Moonstone, I&#x27;ve used a few solicitors over time, working with team at Moonstone has been effortless and efficient, I would be happy to recommend and use again.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">It’s clear that client care and hospitality are taken seriously here. I would highly recommend Moonstone to anyone looking for a professional, welcoming and experienced legal firm.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very impressed with their experience from start to finish. The legal team were exceptionally friendly, welcoming, and professional throughout. The security staff were particularly polite and approachable, making visitors feel comfortable as soon as they arrived. </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">There are two stand-out individuals I feel it is necessary to mention. I have had the pleasure of working with both Andrew Morgan and Darren Morgan as part of the legal team on a recent trial. It has been clear throughout my time working with them that the client feels entirely at ease with each of them – they are trusted and have a way of ensuring the clie</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">LUgandae Patel is highly experienced in a range of disputes, often property-related. Darren Morgan brings a very calm air to matters, such that clients have great confidence in his unruffled manner. Yat Wong is particularly experienced in professional negligence matters. Aimee Hutchinson has a wide range of experience including in judicial review matters arising</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">LUgandae Patel is stand out. Very ‘savvy’. Sound judgment. On top of the issues. Deploys commercial outlook. Excellent client dealing skills.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Commercial Dispute Resolution Client</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"section_team\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"slider-main_component\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-4-card-slider\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_instance\"><h2 data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h2\">Experts in every area</h2><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slid